\chapter{Conclusion}
%
The triangle area technique extracts correlations between two distinct features within traffic records. Therefore proposed system will use triangle area based multivariate correlation technique. Also it will use support vector machine classifier which will classify attacks from legitimate network traffic. The performance of this method is improved and evaluated using normalized dataset. By using the triangle area technique speed up the process of multivariate correlation analysis. This method will produce better performance in terms of speed and accuracy.

In future I will use most sophisticated techniques for classification.As future work i can also provide prevention for the system.
